// pso_widescreen.rc — embeds the compressed boot/intro clips INTO pso_widescreen.asi
// so the videos ship inside the ASI: no loose .mp4 is distributed and the decoder
// never falls back to a file (see mod_video.c vid_embedded_bytes / vid_mf_open_inner).
// The boot-poster PNG stays a loose, swappable file (mod_boot_poster.c) by design.
//
// Resource names are the clip basenames (upper-cased); mod_video maps the configured
// VideoPath/VideoBootPath basename to the matching resource. Paths are relative to
// this .rc (the asi build dir) and point at the in-repo clips in asi/video/
// (Git LFS-tracked, see .gitattributes) so a clean checkout rebuilds WITH the intros.

PSO_BOOTSEQ_16X9 RCDATA "video\\pso_bootseq_16x9.mp4"
PSO_BOOTSEQ_4X3  RCDATA "video\\pso_bootseq_4x3.mp4"
PSO_INTROS_16X9  RCDATA "video\\pso_intros_16x9.mp4"
PSO_INTROS_4X3   RCDATA "video\\pso_intros_4x3.mp4"
